long.am,ar,bg,bn,ca,cs,da,de,el,en,en_AU,en_G:
The Oracle of Thabes is a browser extension that uses local AI models to summarize the contents and answer questions about your open tabs.

It uses the built-in Chrome AI models - your data is not sent to any server it's all free and will work offline.
